  Upstream:   https://www.nethack.org/
              https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack
  Installed:  via the Debian "nethack-console" package (see Dockerfile).
  Source:     The complete, corresponding machine-readable source for the
              packaged binary is available from the Debian source archive
              (the "nethack" source package) and from the upstream sites above.
  Modified:   No. late.sh runs the unmodified distribution binary. It does not
              patch, recompile, or alter NetHack's source or data files.

